            <li>Immutable blockchain proof prevents credential forgery and tampering</li>
            <li>Instant verification via public URLs eliminates manual verification processes</li>
            <li>Visual badge designer enables branded credentials without technical expertise</li>
            <li>Bulk issuance capabilities support efficient distribution to large groups</li>
            <li>Revocation functionality maintains institutional control over credential validity</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <h3><strong>Implementation for Institutions</strong></h3>
        <p>
          Getting started with Blockchain Badges requires no blockchain expertise from your institution. Universities and organizations can integrate the platform through API connections or the visual interface, choosing the approach that fits their technical capabilities.
        </p>
